{"tid":2348770,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"譚耀豪接替梁卓然 執掌刑事檢控科","createTime":"2021-01-01T04:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T16:31:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"aeac6bfc2beacce184b1264beca234f9b0b0481b","tid":2348770,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:28:07.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】副刑事檢控專員譚耀豪接替離任的梁卓然，執掌刑事檢控科。<br />\n<br />\n律政司網站顯示，譚耀豪為署理刑事檢控專員，而原本五名副刑事檢控專員人事亦有變動，萬德豪及黎劍華出任署理副刑事檢控專員。<br />\n<br />\n接替梁卓然的譚耀豪，1994年加入當時的律政署，2015年獲委任為資深大律師，過往曾掌管上訴分科，專門在上訴法庭及終審法院執行檢控上訴案件。<br />\n<br />\n而梁卓然去年7月呈辭，曾透露與律政司司長鄭若驊意見不合，在12月31日離任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418666&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=10da7841\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418666&h=1cd73c1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418666</a>"},{"pid":"d5f84494ac4e8f4cf42f1f19ed6f323554c9792b","tid":2348770,"uid":305767,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩差別"},{"pid":"a78c72d845920232acb8c59f03141102898dae49","tid":2348770,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5f84494ac4e8f4cf42f1f19ed6f323554c9792b","tid":2348770,"uid":305767,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩差別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:29:33.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"4c9468d0c25140de13cc40743286c12b8da8d70d","tid":2348770,"uid":305767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733699fecf754e018ce3ab